## 11. Implementation Priority Checklist

If you can only change 10 things, do these in order:

1. **Switch headline font** to a premium display serif in regular weight
2. **Desaturate and warm your color palette** (green → sage, dark bg → forest green)
3. **Double all section vertical padding** (aim for 120–160px)
4. **Shorten the hero headline** to 4–5 words maximum
5. **Add the social proof / trust metrics bar** below the hero
6. **Adopt alternating zigzag layout** for feature sections
7. **Use off-white** (`#F5F3F0`) instead of pure white for light sections
8. **Simplify the "How it works" section** — one step per section or fewer elements visible at once
9. **Standardize buttons to pill shape**, reduce total button count per viewport
10. **Add slow, subtle scroll-triggered fade-in animations**

